snippet.title: Aquaman (2018) Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard Movie
snippet.description:
▿Aquaman 2018▿

Aquaman is a fictional superhero appearing in comic books published by DC Comics. Created by Mort Weisinger and Paul Norris.

Aquaman finds himself caught between a surface world that a ravages the underwater Atlanteans and the sea who are ready to revolt.

Aquaman has been featured in several adaptations, first appearing in animated form in the 1967. The Superman/Aquaman Hour of Adventure and then in the related Super Friends program. Within the DC Extended Universe, American actor Jason Momoa portrayed the character in the films Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016) and Justice League (2017). Momoa will reprise his role in the upcoming solo film Aquaman, scheduled for release in 2018.
